    "short_sha": "11e62a3",
    "message": "refactor: 统一复用ViewHolder类，移除冗余内部ViewHolder定义\n\n将多个RecyclerView.Adapter的内部ViewHolder类替换为导入的com.mio.ui.adapter.ViewHolder，删除重复的ViewHolder定义代码，精简适配器代码结构",
